{
  "stem": "2581.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because we didn't see those that were taken to [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Chelmno. ?] These were taken to the city of Lodz to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it didn't take too long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, at that time, everything, you know-- every day was like a year.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But looking at it now, this-- these transports we saw in May, and in August, they came to deport our town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'44.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] No, of course, it's August of '42.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm too far already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's '42.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was so sad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We heard.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We prepared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What did we prepare?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My-- my father made me sort of a blouse with a zipper, you know, that I should be able to wear a suit underneath and hide it, and on top, a navy blue blouse.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[SIGHS] For my brother, my father made a suit from the fabric that we had, which wasn't for children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a very expensive fabric.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And on Saturday, I-- you know we-- he wore the suit and we went walking within the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So it was so small that we went to visit a man that used to work for my father, and he had a garden.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And like I said, my-- my younger brother, he was a lively boy and he didn't go through the gate, outside, but he had to climb the-- the fence.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he tore his jacket in the back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the reason I'm telling you this story-- there is a reason why I'm telling you this story.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So of course, this man that worked for my father, he fixed that jacket.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, in the ghetto, when I knew my brother, you know, was already, you know, taken with my mother, and I was assistant foreman in the juvenile part of the factory.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
